rows.label: qst400104_msg0001
rows.name:
Hello there, friend Rex!
Iruiru, proprietor of Whiteside
Salvaging, at your service!

rows.label: qst400104_msg0002
rows.name:
No need for introductions with me,
Iruiru. I was thinking of going to check
out some cylinders in a bit.

rows.label: qst400104_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, that perfect timing! Iruiru just
get in brand-new cylinder type.
If having time, friend want to test out?

rows.label: qst400104_msg0005
rows.name:
Rex is up-and-coming star of salvager
world. If Rex approve of quality, easier
for Iruiru to sell!

rows.label: qst400104_msg0006
rows.name:
It's not every day you get the chance
to test out a brand-new product.
I'd be glad to help!

rows.label: qst400104_msg0007
rows.name:
Then it settled!
Come see Iruiru on rear deck shortly
then. Iruiru will make preparation!
